snippet: Venus Williams, the tennis champion who has her own clothing line, EleVen, takes fashion seriously.
abstract: Tennis champion Venus Williams, who has her own clothing line EleVen, describes the outfits she wore throughout one week. Photo (M)1
lead_paragraph: Venus Williams, 31, has won 43 Women's Tennis Association tour titles, including 7 singles Grand Slams. Ms. Williams grew up in Compton, Calif., and lives in Palm Beach Gardens, Fla., where she recently reintroduced her tennis apparel line, EleVen.BEE-SHYUAN CHANG WEDNESDAY, APRIL 25
